# Rocket.new — Billing & Tokens (Expert Reference)

## Plans at a Glance
| Plan | Price | Monthly Tokens | Figma Screens | Private? | Fix It Free? |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Starter** | Free | 1M ONE-TIME | 2 | ❌ Public | ❌ |
| **Personal** | $25/mo | 5M | 6 | ✅ | ✅ |
| **Rocket** | $50/mo | 10.5M (500K bonus) | 12 | ✅ | ✅ |
| **Booster** | $100/mo | 22M (2M bonus) | 25 | ✅ | ✅ |
| Annual billing | -20% | same | same | ✅ | ✅ |

## Token Types
| Type | Description | Expires? |
|---|---|---|
| **Subscription tokens** | Included in monthly plan | At cancellation |
| **Bonus tokens** | Auto-granted with Rocket/Booster plans | At cancellation |
| **Refuel tokens** | One-time purchase ($20 = 5M) | At cancellation |

## Rollover Policy
- **Monthly paid**: Unused tokens roll over indefinitely month-to-month ✅
- **Annual plans**: Roll over within 12-month term only — at renewal, ALL remaining tokens expire, fresh balance starts
- **Starter**: One-time 1M, never replenishes ❌
- **Cancellation**: ALL token types expire at end of current billing cycle

