## 🔴 The Starter Token Trap (Most Complained-About Issue)

### What Users Expect vs Reality
- **Expectation**: "I have 1M free tokens to build my app"
- **Reality**: 1M tokens is one-time only. Runs out in 2–4 build sessions for anything beyond a basic landing page.

### What 1M Tokens Covers (Roughly)
| Task | Token Cost |
|---|---|
| Generate initial landing page | ~200K–300K |
| Add 2 more pages | ~200K–300K |
| Connect a contact form | ~100K |
| One bug fix cycle | ~50K–150K |
| **Total** | **~600K–850K → nearly gone** |

**Conclusion**: 1M is a demo amount, not enough for a production app.

**Reality**: 1M tokens is enough to demo the platform, not to build a production app. Users who hit zero on Starter need to upgrade to Personal ($25/mo) to get a monthly token refresh.

